A view of a vast expanse of hillsides covered with solar panels in Antu county, Northeast China's Jilin Province, on Saturday. Responding to China's call for green development, Antu is taking advantage of its abundant sunshine and set up solar panels in its hills to realize renewable energy utilization, which benefits the economy and environment at the same time. Photo: IC 
